 Ausf\u00fchrung der Ballonfahrten und mehr\u2026[\/vc_column_text]<div class=\"vcex-spacing wpex-w-100 wpex-clear\" style=\"height:60px;\"><\/div><div class=\"vcex-heading vcex-module wpex-text-2xl wpex-font-normal wpex-m-auto wpex-max-w-100 vcex-heading-plain wpex-block\" data-wpex-hover=\"{&quot;color&quot;:&quot;#000000&quot;}\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&#039;Roboto&#039;,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"vcex-heading-inner wpex-inline-block wpex-clr\">Wenn sie Fragen haben,...<\/span><\/div><div class=\"vcex-spacing wpex-w-100 wpex-clear\"><\/div>[vc_column_text font_family=&#8220;Roboto&#8220; color=&#8220;#000000&#8243; font_size=&#8220;15&#8243;]\u2026 dann schreiben Sie uns doch eine E-Mail oder rufen Sie uns an unter +49 (0) 71 27 \/ 21 173. Gerne k\u00f6nnen Sie uns auch eine Anfrage \u00fcber das <a href=\"http:\/\/www.ballonsport-krohmer.de\/kontakt\"><u>Kontaktformular<\/u><\/a> schreiben.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8220;2\/6&#8243; el_class=&#8220;fixed-sidebar&#8220; css=&#8220;.vc_custom_1563409447358{padding-left: 10% !important;}&#8220;]<div class=\"vcex-heading vcex-module wpex-text-2xl wpex-font-normal wpex-m-auto wpex-max-w-100 vcex-heading-plain wpex-block\" style=\"color:#de8100;font-family:&#039;Roboto&#039;,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"vcex-heading-inner wpex-inline-block wpex-clr\">Ballonsport Krohmer<\/span><\/div><div class=\"vcex-spacing wpex-w-100 wpex-clear\"><\/div>[vc_column_text font_size=&#8220;15&#8243;]Carl-Zeiss-Stra\u00dfe 3<br \/>\n72124 Pliezhausen<\/p>\n<p>T. +49 (0) 71 27 \/ 21 173<br \/>\nFax +49 (0) 7127 18 09-11<br \/>\nM. <a href=\"mailto:info@ballonsport-krohmer.de\">info@ballonsport-krohmer.de<\/a>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row full_width=&#8220;stretch_row&#8220; remove_bottom_col_margin=&#8220;true&#8220; wpex_bg_position=&#8220;center center&#8220;][vc_column][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8220;stretch_row&#8220